sentences.english: Some of them are spaceships from outer space.
sentences.chinese: 有些不明飛行物是外太空來訪的太空船。

sentences.english: Tonight I'm going to talk about the most basic aspect of survival-the space suit.
sentences.chinese: 今天我會講一些基礎的外太空生活的事情，宇航服。

sentences.english: Star Citizen is a multi-player Internet video game set in outer space.
sentences.chinese: 星際公民是一款背景設定於外太空的多玩家網絡遊戲。

sentences.english: Someone thought the USO may come from the outer space.
sentences.chinese: 也有人認爲，這些幽靈潛艇其實是來自外太空。

sentences.english: What if these intelligent aliens are friendly?
sentences.chinese: 如果這些高智慧的外太空生物時友好的呢？

sentences.english: Did Sir Arthur believe in extra- terrestrials?
sentences.chinese: 阿瑟爵士相信外太空生命嗎？

sentences.english: 2125 – Hungary will receive signals from space.
sentences.chinese: 2125年，匈牙利收到外太空的信號。

sentences.english: We have conquered the uter space, but not our inner space.
sentences.chinese: 我們可以征服外太空，但卻征服不了我們的內心。

sentences.english: Strange creatures are wiggling their way down from outerspace.
sentences.chinese: 奇怪的生物正從外太空晃晃悠悠地下來。

sentences.english: I have seen amazing things out there in space.
sentences.chinese: 我曾見識過外太空波瀾萬丈的神奇事物。

sentences.english: Imagine that you and I go in outer space.
sentences.chinese: 設想一下你和我將去到外太空。

sentences.english: He looks at me as though I’m fromouter space.
sentences.chinese: 他看着我，好像我是來自外太空似的。

sentences.english: The journey to outer space and other planets is not a dream any more.
sentences.chinese: 到外太空和其他行星的旅程不再是夢。

definition: celestial body (e.g. planet, satellite etc)/heavenly body
Star Trek (US TV and film series)
